{
  "stem": "9963.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we had to work for several days till the snow stopped.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had to work on the-- the thing to clean the snow off where the trains could go through.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because they were very busy, you know, with the soldiers, transporting different ways.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then later, you know, the-- the different works we had to-- to do in the city-- finally, December the 12th, that-- a few-- a few days before, they give out-- how to say this in English-- you know, the-- what-- we had to be on a place-- and mine age-- that is from 18 years to 25 years.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had to be on a place what they will take us to work in a camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they promised us they will give-- pay us, they will treat us good.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we will have nothing what to worry about.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We had no choice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But they threatened us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "If we won't come over there, they'll find somebody that age group that will kill us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So we went over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They put us on a truck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "That was December the 12th what they took us away from home to a-- the first labor camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And that was [NON-ENGLISH], not far from [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, that was not the last time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I'd worked in a camp what on every Sunday, I'd run away from camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I came home, because I had to take a bath and things like this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that's in-- although you see, that was-- the first camp, we were working over there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we thought if we finished the work, they would let us go, they will send us back home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it wasn't so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So soon if we-- didn't even finish the work, because it got frozen so hard-- the ground.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
